975}, {"id": 322630, "content": "不要硬找话题尬聊，你觉得自己有意思，其实对方觉得你无聊透顶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557878}, {"id": 322379, "content": "化不化妆要你管？", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417126}, {"id": 322649, "content": "去西餐厅已经过时了，撸个串吧。去西餐厅已经过时了，撸个串吧。去西餐厅已经过时了，撸个串吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557959}, {"id": 323165, "content": "感情是处出来，慢慢来，我从不相信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475387}, {"id": 322404, "content": "说拒绝死缠烂打千里寻人的，也别问ta怎么就不追了这种nc问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411759}, {"id": 322415, "content": "死缠烂打依然有效，说无效的是没人缠。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329728}, {"id": 322422, "content": "让男生保持追逐感", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609486}, {"id": 322424, "content": "我个人还挺吃老一套的，关键还是看是否真的喜欢吧\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 322428, "content": "吃饭看电影就咋滴咋滴", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251415}, {"id": 322429, "content": "那一套固定的“流程”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191455}, {"id": 322430, "content": "看星星😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510465}, {"id": 322431, "content": "酒吧=过夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 322432, "content": "舔🐶最后一无所有", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 537958}, {"id": 322436, "content": "无论对方喜不喜欢自己，吻了再说，反正自己又没吃亏，还有可能赚了个女朋友。这种建议希望少点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957543}, {"id": 322439, "content": "做人口普查，把对方各方面情况摸底，问东问西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174172}, {"id": 322442, "content": "没话说选择沉默要好过强聊。",